data.text:
I’m a retired 40-year veteran of TV news, spending my career in Washington, DC and New York with a stint in Cockeysville. I would describe my politics as a complete mess, as my views span the political spectrum depending on the issue. I’ve been a registered Independent since I was old enough to vote. I’m a native New Yorker, born and raised in the South Bronx and Queens. I’ve lived in Manhattan, as well as Arkansas and Maryland.

I’ve hung out with Son of Sam. I play the guitar poorly.
